@IngestionService_HostAddress = http://localhost:5500
@AuthService_HostAddress = http://localhost:5300

### Log in first — the retrieval endpoints require a bearer token.
# @name login
POST {{AuthService_HostAddress}}/auth/v1/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@proptrack.local",
  "password": "ChangeMe123!"
}

###
@token = {{login.response.body.data.accessToken}}

### Semantic search — top-k chunks by cosine similarity (dealId/documentId optional filters)
POST {{IngestionService_HostAddress}}/ingestion/v1/search
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "were any environmental conditions identified?",
  "dealId": "e06e3cce-2188-432b-9d9c-1ecaf62c6db2",
  "topK": 5
}

### Search scoped to a single document
POST {{IngestionService_HostAddress}}/ingestion/v1/search
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "asking price and due diligence period",
  "documentId": "REPLACE_WITH_DOCUMENT_ID",
  "topK": 3
}

### Parsed markdown artifact for a document (what ai-service will summarise from)
GET {{IngestionService_HostAddress}}/ingestion/v1/documents/REPLACE_WITH_DOCUMENT_ID/parsed
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Health — DB + LiteLLM reachability (no auth)
GET {{IngestionService_HostAddress}}/health
